{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.1","label":"","reference":"Job 42:1","prev_osis_id":"Job.041.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Humiliation et repentir de Job<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. Job 39:34-38. (\u00c9s 6:1-5; 57:15.) Da 4:34-37.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Job r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.2","name":"Job 42:2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.41.25","name":"Job 41:25","id":"fra-LSG:Job.41.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.2","label":"","reference":"Job 42:2","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.42.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Je reconnais que tu peux tout,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que rien ne s\u2019oppose \u00e0 tes pens\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.3","name":"Job 42:3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.1","name":"Job 42:1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.3","label":"","reference":"Job 42:3","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.42.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\n    Quel est celui qui a la folie d\u2019obscurcir mes desseins?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Oui, j\u2019ai parl\u00e9, sans les comprendre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    De merveilles qui me d\u00e9passent et que je ne con\u00e7ois pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.4","name":"Job 42:4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.2","name":"Job 42:2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.4","label":"","reference":"Job 42:4","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.42.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>\u00c9coute-moi, et je parlerai;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je t\u2019interrogerai, et tu m\u2019instruiras.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.5","name":"Job 42:5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.3","name":"Job 42:3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.5","label":"","reference":"Job 42:5","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.42.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mon oreille avait entendu parler de toi;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais maintenant mon \u0153il t\u2019a vu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.6","name":"Job 42:6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.4","name":"Job 42:4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.6","label":"","reference":"Job 42:6","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.42.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi je me condamne et je me repens<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sur la poussi\u00e8re et sur la cendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.7","name":"Job 42:7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.5","name":"Job 42:5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.7","label":"","reference":"Job 42:7","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Retour de Job \u00e0 la prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-17: cf. (Ge 20:7, 17. Ja 5:16-18.) (Ja 4:10; 5:11; 1:12.) Ps 30:6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s que l\u2019\u00c9ternel eut adress\u00e9 ces paroles \u00e0 Job, il dit \u00e0 \u00c9liphaz de Th\u00e9man: Ma col\u00e8re est enflamm\u00e9e contre toi et contre tes deux amis, parce que vous n\u2019avez pas parl\u00e9 de moi avec droiture comme l\u2019a fait mon serviteur Job.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.8","name":"Job 42:8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.6","name":"Job 42:6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.8","label":"","reference":"Job 42:8","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Prenez maintenant sept taureaux et sept b\u00e9liers, allez aupr\u00e8s de mon serviteur Job, et offrez pour vous un holocauste. Job, mon serviteur, priera pour vous, et c\u2019est par \u00e9gard pour lui seul que je ne vous traiterai pas selon votre folie; car vous n\u2019avez pas parl\u00e9 de moi avec droiture, comme l\u2019a fait mon serviteur Job.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.9","name":"Job 42:9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.7","name":"Job 42:7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.9","label":"","reference":"Job 42:9","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\u00c9liphaz de Th\u00e9man, Bildad de Schuach, et Tsophar de Naama all\u00e8rent et firent comme l\u2019\u00c9ternel leur avait dit: et l\u2019\u00c9ternel eut \u00e9gard \u00e0 la pri\u00e8re de Job.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.10","name":"Job 42:10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.8","name":"Job 42:8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.10","label":"","reference":"Job 42:10","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel r\u00e9tablit Job dans son premier \u00e9tat, quand Job eut pri\u00e9 pour ses amis; et l\u2019\u00c9ternel lui accorda le double de tout ce qu\u2019il avait poss\u00e9d\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.11","name":"Job 42:11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.9","name":"Job 42:9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.11","label":"","reference":"Job 42:11","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Les fr\u00e8res, les s\u0153urs, et les anciens amis de Job vinrent tous le visiter, et ils mang\u00e8rent avec lui dans sa maison. Ils le plaignirent et le consol\u00e8rent de tous les malheurs que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait fait venir sur lui, et chacun lui donna un kesita et un anneau d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.12","name":"Job 42:12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.10","name":"Job 42:10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.12","label":"","reference":"Job 42:12","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Pendant ses derni\u00e8res ann\u00e9es, Job re\u00e7ut de l\u2019\u00c9ternel plus de b\u00e9n\u00e9dictions qu\u2019il n\u2019en avait re\u00e7u dans les premi\u00e8res. Il poss\u00e9da quatorze mille brebis, six mille chameaux, mille paires de b\u0153ufs, et mille \u00e2nesses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.13","name":"Job 42:13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.11","name":"Job 42:11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.13","label":"","reference":"Job 42:13","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il eut sept fils et trois filles:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.14","name":"Job 42:14","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.12","name":"Job 42:12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.14","label":"","reference":"Job 42:14","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>il donna \u00e0 la premi\u00e8re le nom de Jemima, \u00e0 la seconde celui de Ketsia, et \u00e0 la troisi\u00e8me celui de K\u00e9ren-Happuc.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.15","name":"Job 42:15","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.13","name":"Job 42:13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.15","label":"","reference":"Job 42:15","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il n\u2019y avait pas dans tout le pays d\u2019aussi belles femmes que les filles de Job. Leur p\u00e8re leur accorda une part d\u2019h\u00e9ritage parmi leurs fr\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.16","name":"Job 42:16","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.14","name":"Job 42:14","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.16","label":"","reference":"Job 42:16","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.042.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Job v\u00e9cut apr\u00e8s cela cent quarante ans, et il vit ses fils et les fils de ses fils jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la quatri\u00e8me g\u00e9n\u00e9ration.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.17","name":"Job 42:17","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.15","name":"Job 42:15","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.42.17","label":"","reference":"Job 42:17","prev_osis_id":"Job.042.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.42.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et Job mourut \u00e2g\u00e9 et rassasi\u00e9 de jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.42","name":"Job 42","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.1.1","name":"Psaumes 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.42.16","name":"Job 42:16","id":"fra-LSG:Job.42.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb6259ca7.51487932');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6259ca7.51487932\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 